\c 13
\s Nyika yakasara inogoverwa
\p
\v 1 Zvino Joshua waiva akwegura, ava nemakore mazhinji; Jehovha ndokuti kwaari: Iwe wakwegura, wava nemakore mazhinji, zvino kuchakasara nyika huru kwazvo kugarwa nhaka\x + 23.1; 14.10.\x*.
\v 2 Iyi \add ndiyo\add* nyika yasara\x + Vato. 3.1-4.\x*: Miganhu yose yeVaFirisitia\x + Jow. 3.4; Josh. 22.10,11.\x*, neGeshuri yose\x + 1 Sam. 27.8; 12.5; 11,13.\x*;
\v 3 kubva paShihori iri pamberi peEgipita kusvika kumuganhu weEkironi kumaodzanyemba waiverengerwa kuVaKenani\x + 1 Makor. 13.5. Jer. 2.18.\x*; madzishe mashanu eVaFirisitia\x + Vato. 3.3. 16.30. 1 Sam. 5.8,11. 6.4,12,16,18. 7.7; 29.6,7.\x*: WeGaza, neweAshidhodhi, neweAshikeroni, weGiti, neweEkironi\x + 15.11.\x*, neVaAvhimi\x + Det. 2.23.\x*,
\v 4 kubva kuchamhembe, nyika yose yeVaKenani, neMeara raiva reVaZidhoni, kusvika paAfeki\x + 12.18.\x*, kusvika kumuganhu weVaAmori\x + Vato. 1.34,36.\x*;
\v 5 nenyika yeVaGebhiri, neRebhanoni rose kuenda kumabvazuva\x + 1 Madz. 5.18. Map. 83.7. Eze. 27.9.\x*, kubva paBhaari-Gadhi pajinga pegomo reHemoni\x + 11.17. 12.7.\x*, kusvika pakupinda paHamati\x + Num.. 34.8.\x*.
\v 6 Vagari vose venyika yezvikomo, kubva paRebhanoni kusvika paMisirefoti-Maimi, VaZidhoni vose\x + 11.8.\x*, ini ndichadzinga ivo kubva pamberi pevana vaIsraeri\x + 23.13. Vato. 2.21,23.\x*; koga igovere nemujenya kuIsraeri ku\add i\add*gara nhaka sezvandakakuraira\x + 23.4. Num.. 34.2. Vato. 18.1. Map. 16.6.\x*.
\v 7 Zvino ikozvino, govera nyika iyi kuva nhaka kumarudzi mapfumbamwe nehafu yerudzi rwaManase.
\p
\v 8 Pamwe navo VaRubheni neVaGadhi vakagamuchira nhaka yavo, Mozisi yaakavapa mhiri kwaJoridhani kumabvazuva, Mozisi, muranda waJehovha sezvaakavapa\x + Num.. 32.33. Det. 3.12,13. 29.8. 12.6. 22.4.\x*.
\v 9 Kubva paAroeri riri pamahombekombe erwizi rweArinoni, neguta raiva pakati perwizi\x + Det. 2.36.\x*, nebani rose\x + Det. 3.10.\x* reMedhebha\x + 13.16,17; Num.. 21.30.\x* kusvika paDhibhoni\x + 13.16,17; Num.. 21.30.\x*;
\v 10 nemaguta ose aSihoni mambo weVaAmori waitonga paHeshibhoni\x + Num.. 21.24,25.\x*, kusvika kumuganhu wevana vaAmoni;
\v 11 neGiriyadhi\x + 12.5.\x*, nemuganhu weVaGeshuri neVaMaakati\x + 13.13. Det. 3.14.\x*, negomo rose reHemoni\x + Det. 3.9.\x*, neBhashani rose kusvika paSareka\x + 12.5.\x*;
\v 12 umambo hwose hwaOgi paBhashani, waitonga paAshitaroti nepaEdhirei\x + 12.4.\x*. Ndiye wakasara pamusiiwa weVaRefaimu\x + 12.4.\x*; Mozisi waiva avarovawo ndokuvadzinga panhaka.
\v 13 Zvakadaro vana vaIsraeri havana kudzinga panhaka VaGeshuri neVaMaakati, asi Geshuri neMaakati vagere pakati paIsraeri kusvika nhasi\x + 13.11.\x*.
\v 14 Koga kurudzi rweVaRevhi haana kupa nhaka; zvibairo zvemoto zvaJehovha Mwari waIsraeri ndiyo nhaka yavo\x + Num.. 18.20.\x*, sezvaakataura kwavari\x + 13.33.\x*.
\p
\v 15 Zvino Mozisi wakapa \add mugove\add* kurudzi rwevana vaRubheni nemadzinza avo.
\v 16 Zvino muganhu wavo wakabva paAroeri\x + 13.9.\x* riri pamahombekombe erwizi rweArinoni, neguta riri pakati perwizi, nebani\x + 13.9.\x* rose paMedhebha\x + 13.9.\x*,
\v 17 Heshibhoni nemaguta aro ose ari pabani\x + 13.9.\x*, Dhibhoni\x + 13.9.\x*, neBhamoti-Bhaari, neBheti-Bhaari-Meoni,
\v 18 neJahazi\x + 21.36. 1 Makor. 6.78. Num.. 21.23.\x*, neKedhemoti\x + 21.37. 1 Makor. 6.79.\x*, neMefahati\x + 21.37. 1 Makor. 6.79.\x*,
\v 19 neKiriataimi\x + Num.. 32.37. Eze. 25. 9.\x*, neSibhima, neZereti-Shahari mugomo remupata\x + Num.. 32.38. Isa. 16.8,9. Jer. 48.32.\x*,
\v 20 neBheti-Peori\x + Det.4.46; Num.. 23.28.\x*, neAshidhodhi-Pisiga, neBheti-Jeshimoti\x + 12.3.\x*,
\v 21 nemaguta ose ebani, neumambo hwose hwaSihoni mambo weVaAmori, waitonga paHeshibhoni\x + Det. 3.10.\x*, Mozisi waaiva arova\x + Num.. 21.24.\x* pamwe nevakuru veMidhiani\x + Num.. 31.8.\x*, Evhi, naRekemi, naZuri, naHuri, naRebha, machinda aSihoni, vagari venyika\x + Map. 83.11. Eze. 32.30. Dhan. 11.8. Mik. 5.5.\x*.
\p
\v 22 NaBharamu mwanakomana waBheori\x + Num.. 31.8.\x* muvuki, vana vaIsraeri vakamuuraya nemunondo pakati pevakaurawa navo.
\v 23 Nemuganhu wevana vaRubheni waiva Joridhani nemuganhu \add warwo\add*. Iyi inhaka yevana vaRubheni nemhuri dzavo, maguta nemisha yawo.
\p
\v 24 Zvino Mozisi wakapa \add nhaka\add* kurudzi rwaGadhi, kuvana vaGadhi nemhuri dzavo.
\v 25 Zvino muganhu wavo waiva Jazeri\x + Num.. 21.32; 32.35.\x* nemaguta ose eGiriyadhi nehafu yenyika yevana vaAmoni\x + Num.. 21.26,28,29; Det. 2.19. Vato. 11.13-27.\x*, kusvika paAroeri riri pamberi peRabha\x + Det. 3.11.\x*;
\v 26 uye kubva paHeshibhoni kusvika paRamati-Mizipe neBhetonimu\x + 11.3.\x*, uye kubva paMahanaimu\x + 2 Sam. 17.24.\x* kusvika pamuganhu weDhebhiri\x + 2 Sam. 9.4,5; 17.27.\x*;
\v 27 nemumupata, Bheti-Harami\x + Num.. 32.36.\x*, neBheti-Nimura\x + Num.. 32.3,36.\x*, neSukoti, neZafoni, musarira weumambo hwaSihoni mambo weHeshibhoni, Joridhani nemuganhu \add warwo\x + Gen.. 33.17. 1 Madz. 7.46. 2 Makor. 4.17.\x*\add*, kusvika pamagumisiro egungwa reKinereti, mhiri kwaJoridhani, kumabvazuva\x + Num.. 34.11; 11.2; 12.3.\x*.
\v 28 Iyi inhaka yevana vaGadhi nemhuri dzavo, maguta nemisha yawo.
\p
\v 29 Zvino Mozisi wakapa \add nhaka\add* kuhafu yerudzi rwaManase; uye yaiva yehafu yerudzi rwevana vaManase nemhuri dzavo.
\v 30 Zvino muganhu wavo waibva paMahanaimu, Bhashani rose, umambo hwese hwaOgi mambo weBhashani, nemisha yose yeJairi yaiva paBhashani, maguta makumi matanhatu\x + Det. 3.14. 1 Makor. 2.23. Num.. 32.41.\x*;
\v 31 nehafu yeGiriyadhi, neAshitaroti, neEdhirei, maguta eumambo hwaOgi paBhashani, yaiva yevana vaMakiri\x + 12.4.\x* mwanakomana waManase, yehafu yevana vaMakiri nemhuri dzavo\x + 17.1.\x*.
\v 32 Awa ndiwo Mozisi aakagovera nhaka pamapani aMoabhu mhiri kwaJoridhani paJeriko kumabvazuva\x + Num.. 22.1.\x*.
\p
\v 33 Asi kurudzi rwaRevhi Mozisi haana kupa nhaka\x + 13.14; 18.7.\x*; Jehovha Mwari waIsraeri ndiye nhaka yavo, sezvaakataura kwavari\x + Num.. 18.20.\x*.